snippet.title: Robert's Spooktacular Ghost Train - OUT NOW!
snippet.description:
Go try out the game : https://smoldreamers.itch.io/rsgt
It's "pay what you want", so if you can't or don't want to help us out financially, it's free!

And play our first game "Wherever You Hike" now :
https://smoldreamers.itch.io/wherever-you-hike

Want to support us? Check our patreon : https://www.patreon.com/smoldreamers

We also stream on twitch, every wednesday at 19:00 (7 PM) : https://www.twitch.tv/smoldreamers
